GameSquare
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.ItemSelectable, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.SwingConstants
public abstract class GameSquare
extends javax.swing.JButton
This class provides a representation of a single game square. The class is abstract, and should be extended to provide domain specific functionality.
